data.description: Beautiful home in Bell Pointe 1 is looking for a new owner! Upon arrival, you will be greeted by well-maintained landscaping & a cozy porch where you can sit & enjoy the peaceful neighborhood. The pristine interior features soothing palette complemented w/tasteful flooring - wood & soft carpeting throughout. The spacious living/dining room is accentuated w/a dazzling chandelier, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere. Designed for entertaining gatherings, this bright great room has an immaculate kitchen w/white cabinets, granite counters, SS appliances, a pantry, & a convenient breakfast bar to grab a quick midnight bite. Take advantage of the versatile loft, a private spot for relaxing. The cozy main suite showcases an ensuite w/dual sinks & a walk-in closet. The serene backyard provides a relaxing covered patio, a grassy landscape, & a gazebo that is awesome for al fresco dining. This is a true gem you don't want to miss!
